	<div class="dm-quote-container">
		<hr/>
			<div class="dm-quote">
				... his <b>delight</b> is in the law of the Lord,
				and on his law he <b>meditates</b> day and night.
				<div class="dm-quote-citation">Psalm 1</div>
			</div>
		<hr/>
