	<p>
		<b>Delight/Meditate</b> is a free daily Bible reading web app
		for mobile devices and desktop web browsers.
		It takes you through a daily reading plan
		and is designed to be simple, quick, and frictionless.
		For each reading, you can read your physical Bible
		or, with a single click, view the reading
		at one of the popular online Bible web sites,
		in your chosen translation.
	</p>
	<p>
		<b>Delight/Meditate</b> is a web app - to use it, just visit DelightMeditate.com.
		You don't need to install anything on your device.
	</p>
	<p class="dm-visitor-only">
		For a quick introduction, click <b>Test drive</b> below.
		To learn more, sign up for a free account.
		You can experiment as much as you like.
		It's easy to add or remove plans and to jump around within plans.
	</p>
